g":10407748.0,"float_shares":3662622.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.45601,"held_pct_institutions":0.0,"beta":0.354,"fifty_two_week_high":8.65,"fifty_two_week_low":4.12,"fifty_day_average":6.6386,"two_hundred_day_avg":6.0658,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":8.65,"all_time_low":4.01,"long_business_summary":"Nihar Info Global Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the software and e-commerce businesses in India. It operates through Rendering of Services; Sales of Goods through E-Commerce; and Trading Activities segments. The company sells health, dietary supplements, ayurvedic products, generic medicines, pharmaceuticals, drugs, organic foods, healthcare devices, sports equipment, fitness, baby, mother care, beauty care, wellness, personal care products, pet foods, lifestyle, home, kitchen, travel, storage and organizer, under the ONVO and LIFE108 brands; and computers, accessories, small, large appliances, office, stationery, travel, luggage, audio visual systems, video conferencing solutions, IT hardware, software applications, manpower services, bulk orders, supplies, corporate gifting, and GEM, government orders, as well as electronics, mobiles, tablets, and accessories to corporate and government customers through B2B e-commerce. It also operates Nihar Market e-Center that offers a wide range of products and services; and engages in eCenter franchise operations. In addition, the company is involved in the research and development, design, manufacture, trading, sale, import, and export of computer software and hardware, as well as provision of consultancy services in the field of software development, and turnkey projects and solutions. Further, it provides document management system, business process management, case management, record management, and storage management, as well as data capture automation, collaboration, mailing, archiving, and customized ERP solutions. The company serves the power sector, port, infrastructure, LPO, atomic energy, defense, government, mining, and education industries. It also exports its products to Russia. The company was formerly known as Genesys Securities Ltd and changed its name to Nihar Info Global Limited in October 2003. Nihar Info Global Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Hyderabad, India."}}